// ‚Ėą‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖĄ ‚Ėą ‚ĖÄ ‚ĖÄ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚Ėą
// ‚Ėą ‚ĖÄ ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖĄ‚Ėą ‚Ėą ‚ĖÄ‚Ėą ‚Ėą  ‚Ėą  ‚Ėą‚ĖĄ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚ĖÖ

output "DP-1" {
    mode "2560x1080@200"
    scale 1
    position x=0 y=0
    focus-at-startup
}

hotkey-overlay {
    skip-at-startup
}

// ‚Ėą   ‚ĖĄ‚ĖÄ‚Ėą ‚Ėą ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖĄ ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ ‚Ėą ‚Ėą
// ‚Ėą‚ĖĄ‚ĖĄ ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖÖ‚Ėą ‚Ėą ‚ĖÄ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖÖ‚ĖÖ ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚Ėą

spawn-at-startup "dbus-update-activation-environment" "--systemd" "DISPLAY" "WAYLAND_DISPLAY" "XDG_CURRENT_DESKTOP=GNOME"
spawn-at-startup "systemctl" "--user" "import-environment" "DISPLAY" "WAYLAND_DISPLAY" "XDG_CURRENT_DESKTOP" "XDG_SESSION_DESKTOP" "XDG_SESSION_TYPE"
spawn-at-startup "waypaper" "--restore"
spawn-at-startup "swaync"
spawn-at-startup "waybar"
spawn-at-startup "systemctl" "--user" "start" "plasma-polkit-agent.service"
spawn-at-startup "wl-clip-persist" "--clipboard" "both"
spawn-at-startup "env" "CLIPHIST_MAX_ITEMS=50" "wl-paste" "--type" "text" "--watch" "cliphist" "store"
spawn-at-startup "env" "CLIPHIST_MAX_ITEMS=50" "wl-paste" "--type" "image" "--watch" "cliphist" "store"
spawn-at-startup "XDG_CURRENT_DESKTOP=gnome" "64gram-desktop" "-startintray"
spawn-at-startup "steam" "-silent"
//spawn-at-startup "easyeffects" "--hide-window" "--service-mode"
spawn-at-startup "bash" "-c" "'XDG_MENU_PREFIX=arch-" "kbuildsycoca6'"
//spawn-at-startup "rm" "-rf" "~/.cache/cliphist/db"

// ‚Ėą ‚Ėą ‚ĖĄ‚ĖÄ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚Ėą ‚ĖÄ ‚ĖĄ‚ĖÄ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚Ėā‚Ėā ‚Ėą   ‚ĖÖ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĄ
// ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÖ‚ĖÄ ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚ĖÖ ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚Ėā‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖĄ‚ĖĄ ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĄ‚Ėā‚ĖĒ

environment {
    // Appearance
    QT_QPA_PLATFORMTHEME "qt6ct"
    QT_WAYLAND_DISABLE_WINDOWDECORATION "1"
    QT_AUTO_SCREEN_SCALE_FACTOR "1"
    QT_SCALE_FACTOR "1"

    // Cursor
    XCURSOR_THEME "Moga-Candy-Macchiato"
    XCURSOR_SIZE "18"

    // IMPORTANT
    GTK_USE_PORTAL "1"
    QT_QPA_PLATFORM "wayland;xcb"

    // Problem Fix
    XDG_SESSION_TYPE "wayland"
    ELECTRON_OZONE_PLATFORM_HINT "wayland"
    CLUTTER_BACKEND "wayland"
    ELECTRON_ENABLE_WAYLAND "1"
    MOZ_ENABLE_WAYLAND "1"
    MOZ_DISABLE_RDD_SANDBOX "1"
    SDL_VIDEODRIVER "wayland"
    DISABLE_LAYER_AMD_SWITCHABLE_GRAPHICS_1 "1"

    // Hardware
    GBM_BACKEND "nvidia-drm"
    NVD_BACKEND "direct"
    __GLX_VENDOR_LIBRARY_NAME "nvidia"
    LIBVA_DRIVER_NAME "nvidia"
    __GL_VRR_ALLOWED "1"
    __GL_THREADED_OPTIMIZATIONS "1"
}

xwayland-satellite {
    on
    path "xwayland-satellite"
}

// ‚Ėą ‚Ėą ‚ĖÄ ‚Ėą‚ĖĒ‚ĖĒ ‚Ėą ‚Ėą ‚ĖĄ‚ĖÄ‚Ėą ‚Ėą
// ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÖ‚ĖÄ ‚Ėą ‚Ėā‚Ėā‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚Ėā‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖĄ‚ĖĄ

window-rule {
    geometry-corner-radius 16
    clip-to-geometry true
    opacity 0.94
    background-effect {
        blur true
        xray true
    }
}

blur {
    passes 3
    offset 3
    noise 0.02
}

prefer-no-csd

layout {
    always-center-single-column
    gaps 12
    center-focused-column "never"
  //center-focused-column "always"
    preset-column-widths {
        proportion 0.33333
        proportion 0.5
        proportion 0.66667
    }

    default-column-width { proportion 0.5; }

    focus-ring {
        width 0
    }

    border {
        on
        width 1
        active-color "#00000023"
        inactive-color "#00000000"
    }

    shadow {
        on
        softness 14
        spread 2
        offset x=0 y=3
        color "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55)"
    }

    struts {
        left 5
        right 5
        bottom 3
        top -11
    }
}

// ‚Ėą‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚Ėą ‚ĖÄ ‚Ėą‚ĖĒ‚ĖĒ ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ
// ‚Ėą ‚ĖÄ ‚Ėą ‚Ėą ‚Ėā‚Ėā‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖÖ‚ĖÖ

animations {

    workspace-switch {
        spring damping-ratio=1.6 stiffness=5000 epsilon=0.0001
    }

    window-open {
        duration-ms 150
        curve "ease-out-expo"
    }

    window-close {
        duration-ms 150
        curve "ease-out-quad"
    }

    horizontal-view-movement {
        spring damping-ratio=1.0 stiffness=800 epsilon=0.0001
    }

    window-movement {
        spring damping-ratio=1.0 stiffness=800 epsilon=0.0001
    }

    window-resize {
        spring damping-ratio=1.0 stiffness=800 epsilon=0.0001
    }

    config-notification-open-close {
        spring damping-ratio=0.6 stiffness=1000 epsilon=0.001
    }

    exit-confirmation-open-close {
        spring damping-ratio=0.6 stiffness=500 epsilon=0.01
    }

    screenshot-ui-open {
        duration-ms 200
        curve "ease-out-quad"
    }

    overview-open-close {
        spring damping-ratio=1.0 stiffness=800 epsilon=0.0001
    }

    recent-windows-close {
        spring damping-ratio=1.0 stiffness=800 epsilon=0.001
    }
}

// ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖĄ ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚Ėą ‚Ėą ‚Ėą ‚ĖÄ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ
// ‚Ėą ‚Ėą ‚ĖÄ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ ‚Ėą‚ĖÖ‚Ėą  ‚Ėą

gestures {
    hot-corners { 
        off;
    }
}

input {
    keyboard {
        xkb {
            layout "us,ru"
            options "grp:alt_shift_toggle"
        }
        numlock
    }

    touchpad {
        off
        tap
        natural-scroll
    }

    mouse {
        accel-speed -0.78
        accel-profile "flat"
        scroll-method "no-scroll"
        natural-scroll
    }   
    focus-follows-mouse max-scroll-amount="20%"

    trackpoint {
        off
    }   
}

// ‚Ėą‚ĖÉ‚ĖÄ ‚ĖÖ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĄ ‚Ėą ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚Ėā‚Ėā ‚ĖÄ ‚Ėą‚ĖĄ ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚ĖĄ ‚Ėą‚ĖĒ‚ĖĒ
// ‚Ėą‚ĖÄ‚ĖĄ ‚ĖÄ‚ĖĄ‚Ėā‚ĖĒ   ‚Ėą  ‚Ėą‚Ėā‚Ėą ‚Ėą ‚Ėą ‚ĖÄ‚Ėą ‚Ėą‚ĖÉ‚ĖÄ ‚Ėā‚Ėā‚Ėą

binds {
    Mod+Shift+Slash { show-hotkey-overlay; }
    
    Super+w hotkey-overlay-title="Open a Terminal: Kitty" { spawn "kitty"; }
    Super+r hotkey-overlay-title="Wofi" { spawn "wofi" "--show run" ; }
    Super+z hotkey-overlay-title="zen-browser" { spawn "zen-browser"; }
    Super+e { spawn "dolphin"; }
    Super+I hotkey-overlay-title="waypaper" { spawn "waypaper"; }
    Alt+Z { spawn-sh "gsr-ui-cli toggle-show"; }
    Super+V hotkey-overlay-title="Clipboard History" {
         spawn "sh" "-c" "cliphist list | wofi --dmenu | cliphist decode | wl-copy && wl-paste -t text/plain | xclip -selection clipboard"
    }
    Ctrl+Alt+S hotkey-overlay-title="hyprpicker" { spawn "hyprpicker" "--autocopy"; }
    Super+Alt+L hotkey-overlay-title="Lock the Screen: swaylock" { spawn "swaylock"; }

    Super+Alt+S allow-when-locked=true hotkey-overlay-title=null { spawn-sh "pkill orca || exec orca"; }
 
    Super+Q repeat=false { close-window; }
    Super+S { toggle-window-floating; } 
    Super+F { fullscreen-window; }
    Super+Shift+F { maximize-column; }
    Super+X { set-column-width "50%"; }

    Ctrl+Alt+Delete { quit; }
    Super+Tab repeat=false { toggle-overview; }

    Super+A { focus-column-left; }
    Super+D { focus-column-right; }
    Super+WheelScrollUp { focus-column-right; }
    Super+WheelScrollDown { focus-column-left; }
    Super+Shift+D  { move-column-right; }
    Super+Shift+A  { move-column-left; }

    Super+Shift+S { screenshot; }
    Print { screenshot-screen; }

    Super+1 { focus-workspace 1; }
    Super+2 { focus-workspace 2; }
    Super+3 { focus-workspace 3; }
    Super+4 { focus-workspace 4; }
    Super+5 { focus-workspace 5; }
    Super+Shift+1 { move-column-to-workspace 1; }
    Super+Shift+2 { move-column-to-workspace 2; }
    Super+Shift+3 { move-column-to-workspace 3; }
    Super+Shift+4 { move-column-to-workspace 4; }
    Super+Shift+5 { move-column-to-workspace 5; }

    XF86AudioRaiseVolume allow-when-locked=true { spawn-sh "wpctl set-volume @DEFAULT_AUDIO_SINK@ 0.1+ -l 1.0"; }
    XF86AudioLowerVolume allow-when-locked=true { spawn-sh "wpctl set-volume @DEFAULT_AUDIO_SINK@ 0.1-"; }
    XF86AudioMute        allow-when-locked=true { spawn-sh "wpctl set-mute @DEFAULT_AUDIO_SINK@ toggle"; }
    XF86AudioMicMute     allow-when-locked=true { spawn-sh "wpctl set-mute @DEFAULT_AUDIO_SOURCE@ toggle"; }
    XF86AudioPlay        allow-when-locked=true { spawn-sh "playerctl play-pause"; }
    XF86AudioStop        allow-when-locked=true { spawn-sh "playerctl stop"; }
    XF86AudioPrev        allow-when-locked=true { spawn-sh "playerctl previous"; }
    XF86AudioNext        allow-when-locked=true { spawn-sh "playerctl next"; }
}

include "windowrule.kdl"
